{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The anger in me against corruption"},{"time":4000,"text":"made me to make a big career change"},{"time":7000,"text":"last year, becoming a full-time practicing lawyer."},{"time":11000,"text":"My experiences over the last 18 months,"},{"time":15000,"text":"as a lawyer, has seeded in me"},{"time":17000,"text":"a new entrepreneurial idea,"},{"time":20000,"text":"which I believe is indeed"},{"time":22000,"text":"worth spreading."},{"time":24000,"text":"So, I share it with all of you here today,"},{"time":27000,"text":"though the idea itself is getting crystallized"},{"time":29000,"text":"and I'm still writing up the business plan."},{"time":32000,"text":"Of course it helps that fear of public failure"},{"time":35000,"text":"diminishes as the number of ideas"},{"time":38000,"text":"which have failed increases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"I've been a huge fan of enterprise and entrepreneurship"},{"time":45000,"text":"since 1993."},{"time":47000,"text":"I've explored, experienced,"},{"time":49000,"text":"and experimented enterprise"},{"time":51000,"text":"and capitalism to my heart's content."},{"time":54000,"text":"I built, along with my two brothers,"},{"time":56000,"text":"the leading real estate company in my home state, Kerala,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and then worked professionally"},{"time":62000,"text":"with two of India's biggest businessmen,"},{"time":65000,"text":"but in their startup enterprises."},{"time":68000,"text":"In 2003, when I stepped out of the pure play capitalistic sector"},{"time":73000,"text":"to work on so-called social sector issues,"},{"time":77000,"text":"I definitely did not have any grand strategy"},{"time":81000,"text":"or plan to pursue and find"},{"time":84000,"text":"for-profit solutions"},{"time":86000,"text":"to addressing pressing public issues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"When life brought about a series"},{"time":91000,"text":"of death and near-death experiences"},{"time":94000,"text":"within my close circle,"},{"time":96000,"text":"which highlighted the need"},{"time":98000,"text":"for an emergency medical response service in India,"},{"time":101000,"text":"similar to 911 in USA."},{"time":104000,"text":"To address this, I, along with four friends,"},{"time":107000,"text":"founded Ambulance Access for All,"},{"time":109000,"text":"to promote life-support ambulance services in India."},{"time":113000,"text":"For those from the developing world,"},{"time":115000,"text":"there is nothing, absolutely nothing new in this idea."},{"time":118000,"text":"But as we envisioned it,"},{"time":120000,"text":"we had three key goals:"},{"time":122000,"text":"Providing world-class life support ambulance service"},{"time":125000,"text":"which is fully self-sustainable from its own revenue streams,"},{"time":128000,"text":"and universally accessible"},{"time":130000,"text":"to anyone in a medical emergency,"},{"time":133000,"text":"irrespective of the capability to pay."},{"time":136000,"text":"The service which grew out of this,"},{"time":138000,"text":"Dial 1298 for Ambulance,"},{"time":140000,"text":"with one ambulance in 2004,"},{"time":143000,"text":"now has a hundred-plus ambulances in three states,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and has transported over 100,000 patients"},{"time":149000,"text":"and victims since inception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151000,"text":"The service is -- (Applause)"},{"time":154000,"text":"fully self-sustainable from its own revenues,"},{"time":157000,"text":"without accessing any public funds,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and the cross-subsidy model actually works,"},{"time":163000,"text":"where the rich pays higher, poor pays lower,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and the accident victim is getting the service free of charge."},{"time":170000,"text":"The service responded effectively"},{"time":172000,"text":"and efficiently,"},{"time":174000,"text":"during the unfortunate"},{"time":176000,"text":"26/11 Mumbai terror attacks."},{"time":179000,"text":"And as you can see from the visuals,"},{"time":183000,"text":"the service was responding and rescuing"},{"time":186000,"text":"victims from the incident locations"},{"time":189000,"text":"even before the police could cordon off"},{"time":192000,"text":"the incident locations"},{"time":195000,"text":"and formally confirm it as a terror strike."},{"time":198000,"text":"We ended up being the first medical response team"},{"time":202000,"text":"in every incident location"},{"time":205000,"text":"and transported 125 victims,"},{"time":208000,"text":"saving life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"In tribute and remembrance"},{"time":219000,"text":"of 26/11 attacks"},{"time":223000,"text":"over the last one year,"},{"time":226000,"text":"we have actually helped a Pakistani NGO,"},{"time":229000,"text":"Aman Foundation,"},{"time":232000,"text":"to set up a self-sustainable life support ambulance service"},{"time":236000,"text":"in Karachi, facilitated by Acumen Fund."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"It's a small message from us,"},{"time":249000,"text":"in our own small way"},{"time":251000,"text":"to the enemies of humanity,"},{"time":253000,"text":"of Islam, of South Asia,"},{"time":256000,"text":"of India, and of Pakistan,"},{"time":259000,"text":"that humanity will continue to bloom,"},{"time":262000,"text":"irrespective of such dastardly attacks."},{"time":264000,"text":"Since then I've also co-founded two other social enterprises."},{"time":268000,"text":"One is Education Access for All,"},{"time":270000,"text":"setting up schools in small-town India."},{"time":273000,"text":"And the other is Moksha-Yug Access,"},{"time":275000,"text":"which is integrating rural supply chain"},{"time":277000,"text":"on the foundations of self-help group-based microfinance."},{"time":282000,"text":"I guess we seem to be doing at least a few things right."},{"time":285000,"text":"Because diligent investors and venture funds"},{"time":288000,"text":"have committed over 7.5 million dollars in funding."},{"time":292000,"text":"With the significance being these funds have come in"},{"time":294000,"text":"as a QT capital, not as grant or as philanthropy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"Now I come back to the idea of the new social enterprise"},{"time":301000,"text":"that I'm exploring."},{"time":303000,"text":"Corruption, bribes, and lack of transparency."},{"time":306000,"text":"You may be surprised to know"},{"time":308000,"text":"that eight speakers yesterday"},{"time":311000,"text":"actually mentioned these terms in their talks."},{"time":314000,"text":"Bribes and corruption have both a demand and a supply side,"},{"time":317000,"text":"with the supply side being mostly of"},{"time":320000,"text":"greedy corporate unethical businesses"},{"time":322000,"text":"and hapless common man."},{"time":324000,"text":"And the demand side being mostly politicians,"},{"time":327000,"text":"bureaucrats and those who have discretionary power"},{"time":329000,"text":"vested with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"According to World Bank estimate,"},{"time":333000,"text":"one trillion dollars is paid in bribes"},{"time":336000,"text":"every year, worsening the condition"},{"time":338000,"text":"of the already worse off."},{"time":340000,"text":"Yet, if you analyze the common man,"},{"time":343000,"text":"he or she does not wake up every day and say,"},{"time":346000,"text":"\"Hmm, let me see who I can pay a bribe to today.\""},{"time":349000,"text":"or, \"Let me see who I can corrupt today.\""},{"time":352000,"text":"Often it is the constraining or the back-to-the-wall situation"},{"time":357000,"text":"that the hapless common man finds himself or herself in"},{"time":360000,"text":"that leads him to pay a bribe."},{"time":362000,"text":"In the modern day world, where time is premium"},{"time":365000,"text":"and battle for subsistence is unimaginably tough,"},{"time":368000,"text":"the hapless common man"},{"time":370000,"text":"simply gives in and pays the bribe just to get on with life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"Now, let me ask you another question."},{"time":377000,"text":"Imagine you are being asked to pay a bribe"},{"time":379000,"text":"in your day-to-day life to get something done."},{"time":382000,"text":"What do you do? Of course you can call the police."},{"time":385000,"text":"But what is the use if the police department is in itself steeped in corruption?"},{"time":389000,"text":"Most definitely you don't want to pay the bribe."},{"time":392000,"text":"But you also don't have the time, resources,"},{"time":395000,"text":"expertise or wherewithal to fight this."},{"time":398000,"text":"Unfortunately, many of us in this room"},{"time":402000,"text":"are supporters of capitalist policies and market forces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"Yet the market forces around the world"},{"time":409000,"text":"have not yet thrown up a service where you can call in,"},{"time":412000,"text":"pay a fee, and fight the demand for a bribe."},{"time":415000,"text":"Like a bribe buster service,"},{"time":418000,"text":"or 1-800-Fight-Bribes,"},{"time":420000,"text":"or www.stopbribes.org or"},{"time":424000,"text":"www.preventcorruption.org."},{"time":427000,"text":"Such a service simply do not exist."},{"time":430000,"text":"One image that has haunted me"},{"time":432000,"text":"from my early business days"},{"time":434000,"text":"is of a grandmother, 70 plus years, being harassed"},{"time":437000,"text":"by the bureaucrats in the town planning office."},{"time":440000,"text":"All she needed was permission to build three steps"},{"time":442000,"text":"to her house, from ground level,"},{"time":444000,"text":"making it easier for her to enter and exit her house."},{"time":447000,"text":"Yet the officer in charge would not simply give her the permit"},{"time":450000,"text":"for want of a bribe."},{"time":452000,"text":"Even though it pricked my conscience then,"},{"time":454000,"text":"I could not, or rather I did not"},{"time":456000,"text":"tend to her or assist her,"},{"time":459000,"text":"because I was busy building my real estate company."},{"time":461000,"text":"I don't want to be haunted by such images any more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"A group of us have been working on a pilot basis"},{"time":467000,"text":"to address individual instances of demands"},{"time":470000,"text":"for bribes for common services or entitlement."},{"time":473000,"text":"And in all 42 cases where we have pushed back such demands"},{"time":476000,"text":"using existing and legitimate tools"},{"time":479000,"text":"like the Right to Information Act,"},{"time":481000,"text":"video, audio, or peer pressure,"},{"time":484000,"text":"we have successfully obtained whatever our clients"},{"time":486000,"text":"set out to achieve without actually paying a bribe."},{"time":490000,"text":"And with the cost of these tools being substantially lower"},{"time":493000,"text":"than the bribe demanded."},{"time":495000,"text":"I believe that these tools that worked in these 42 pilot cases"},{"time":500000,"text":"can be consolidated in standard processes"},{"time":504000,"text":"in a BPO kind of environment,"},{"time":507000,"text":"and made available on web, call-center"},{"time":510000,"text":"and franchise physical offices,"},{"time":512000,"text":"for a fee, to serve anyone confronted with a demand for a bribe."},{"time":517000,"text":"The target market is as tempting as it can get."},{"time":520000,"text":"It can be worth up to one trillion dollars,"},{"time":523000,"text":"being paid in bribes every year,"},{"time":525000,"text":"or equal to India's GDP."},{"time":528000,"text":"And it is an absolutely virgin market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531000,"text":"I propose to explore this idea further,"},{"time":534000,"text":"to examine the potential of creating"},{"time":536000,"text":"a for-profit, fee-based BPO"},{"time":540000,"text":"kind of service to stop bribes"},{"time":542000,"text":"and prevent corruption."},{"time":544000,"text":"I do realize that the fight for justice"},{"time":547000,"text":"against corruption is never easy."},{"time":550000,"text":"It never has been and it never will be."},{"time":552000,"text":"In my last 18 months as a lawyer,"},{"time":555000,"text":"battling small- and large-scale corruption,"},{"time":557000,"text":"including the one perpetrated by India's biggest corporate scamster."},{"time":561000,"text":"Through his charities"},{"time":563000,"text":"I have had three police cases filed against me"},{"time":566000,"text":"alleging trespass, impersonation and intimidation."},{"time":569000,"text":"The battle against corruption"},{"time":571000,"text":"exacts a toll on ourselves,"},{"time":573000,"text":"our families, our friends, and even our kids."},{"time":577000,"text":"Yet I believe the price we pay is well worth holding on"},{"time":579000,"text":"to our dignity and making the world a fairer place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"What gives us the courage?"},{"time":585000,"text":"As my close friend replied, when told"},{"time":587000,"text":"during the seeding days of the ambulance project"},{"time":590000,"text":"that it is an impossible task"},{"time":592000,"text":"and the founders are insane to chalk up their blue-chip jobs,"},{"time":595000,"text":"I quote: \"Of course we cannot fail in this,"},{"time":598000,"text":"at least in our own minds."},{"time":600000,"text":"For we are insane people,"},{"time":602000,"text":"trying to do an impossible task."},{"time":604000,"text":"And an insane person does not know what an impossible task is.\" Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"Chris Anderson: Shaffi, that is a really exciting business idea."},{"time":621000,"text":"Shaffi Mather: I just have to get through the initial days where I don't get eliminated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":627000,"text":"CA: What's on your mind?"},{"time":628000,"text":"I mean, give us a sense of the numbers here --"},{"time":630000,"text":"a typical bribe and a typical fee. I mean, what's in your head?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":633000,"text":"SM: So let me ... Let me give you an example."},{"time":637000,"text":"Somebody who had applied for the passport."},{"time":640000,"text":"The officer was just sitting on it"},{"time":643000,"text":"and was demanding around 3,000 rupees in bribes."},{"time":646000,"text":"And he did not want to pay."},{"time":649000,"text":"So we actually used the Right to Information Act,"},{"time":651000,"text":"which is equal to the Freedom of Information Act in the United States,"},{"time":654000,"text":"and pushed back the officers in this particular case."},{"time":659000,"text":"And in all these 42 cases,"},{"time":661000,"text":"when we kept pushing them back,"},{"time":664000,"text":"there was three kinds of reaction."},{"time":666000,"text":"A set of people actually say,"},{"time":668000,"text":"\"Oh, let me just grant it to them, and run away from it.\""},{"time":671000,"text":"Some people actually come back and say,"},{"time":674000,"text":"\"Oh, you want to screw me. Let me show you what I can do.\""},{"time":677000,"text":"And he will push us back."},{"time":679000,"text":"So you take the next step, or use the next tool available"},{"time":683000,"text":"in what we are putting together,"},{"time":685000,"text":"and then he relents."},{"time":688000,"text":"By the third time, in all 42 cases, we have achieved success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"CA: But if it's a 3,000-rupee, 70-dollar bribe,"},{"time":696000,"text":"what fee would you have to charge,"},{"time":698000,"text":"and can you actually make the business work?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":700000,"text":"SM: Well, actually the cost that we incurred"},{"time":704000,"text":"was less than 200 rupees."},{"time":707000,"text":"So, it actually works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710000,"text":"CA: That's a high gross margin business. I like it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":715000,"text":"SM: I actually did not want to answer this on the TED stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718000,"text":"CA: OK, so these are provisional numbers, no pricing guarantee."},{"time":722000,"text":"If you can pull this off, you will be a global hero."},{"time":725000,"text":"I mean, this could be huge."},{"time":727000,"text":"Thank you so much for sharing this idea at TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}